{"type": "article", "id": 29576, "title": "覆有榻榻米的家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-13T23:08:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607132037192ueWXndhEUcRMQjV.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>在法国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.joselevy.fr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">José Lévy</a> 眼中，榻榻米不仅可以作为地板铺就，也可以成为家具的设计元素起到装饰的效果。Moving Tatami 就是他为日本制造商 <a href=\"http://www.daiken-ad.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Daiken</a> 设计的一套家具，包含了沙发、储物柜、边桌、架子。部分表面由榻榻米覆盖，搭配上漆的木材显得十分素颜。为了增强榻榻米的耐用性，Lévy 在制作时还加入了和纸。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607132037370iBD5ZVAcqW9CnYS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713203737hIET1i4wC0QOgFbk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713203738SH6OiUsJZnkFCaN0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713203737QdfMigwan7CryqP4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}